rdp - remote desktop protocil
2 ways:
1 from third party softwate like mobaxterm or putty
and other is go to run command and then type "mstsc"
it opens a rdp then give ip address, at down there is a option called more options
in that select local resources then go to more in properties then go to click on drives 
drives is for accessing the physical drives in virtual machine
then click on more choices give username as "administartor" and give passwd then connect
it conects
